{"word":"G5219 - ὑπακούω - hypakoúō - hoop-ak-oo'-o - Hearken","slug":"G5219","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπακούω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hypakoúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-ak-oo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hearken"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - hupakouo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-ak-oo'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G191\">G191</a>; to <i>hear under</i> (as a <i>subordinate</i>), that is, to <i>listen attentively</i>; by implication to <i>heed</i> or <i>conform</i> to a command or authority: - hearken, be obedient to, obey."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1522\">G1522</a>, <a href=\"#/G1873\">G1873</a>, <a href=\"#/G189\">G189</a>, <a href=\"#/G191\">G191</a>, <a href=\"#/G3876\">G3876</a>, <a href=\"#/G3878\">G3878</a>, <a href=\"#/G5218\">G5218</a>, <a href=\"#/G5255\">G5255</a>"}]}